TY  - JOUR
TI  - THE FOLK THEOREM IN REPEATED GAMES WITH ANONYMOUS RANDOM MATCHING
AU  - Deb, Joyee
AU  - Sugaya, Takuo
AU  - Wolitzky, Alexander
AB  - [We prove the folk theorem for discounted repeated games with anonymous random matching. We allow non-uniform matching, include asymmetric payoffs, and place no restrictions on the stage game other than full dimensionality. No record-keeping or communication devices—including cheap talk communication and public randomization—are necessary.]
